strace : system call tracing per process
strace <command>             : trace command
strace -p    <PID>              : trace process
strace -c    <command>/-p <PID> : count system calls
strace -e    <system_call>      : filter a system calls 
strace -f    <command>/-p <PID> : follow child processes
starce -T    <command>/-p <PID> : print time of  system call
starce -tt  <command>/-p <PID>  : print time (ms) 

ltrace : library call tracing tool
ltrace <command>             : trace command
ltrace -p <PID>              : trace process
ltrace -c <command>/-p <PID> : count library calls
ltrace -e <system_call>      : filter a library call
ltrace -f <command>/-p <PID> : follow child processes
ltrace -S <command>/-p <PID> : add system calls
